Class ClientModel

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.it.galaxytrucker.networking.client.clientmodel.ClientModel
public class ClientModel extends Object
This class is used by clients to store a local version of the game state, as well as information relating to the player themselves (i.e., nickname, game they are in, etc.)
Version:
1.0
Author:
giacomoamaducci
